{"sectionId":672,"sectionIdLiteral":"672","humanId":"lesson-257","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"Let me remember what my purpose is.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 257"},"annotation":"W-257","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-257\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"672#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>If I forget my goal I can be but confused, unsure of what I am, and thus conflicted in my actions.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>No one can serve contradicting goals and serve them well.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Nor can he function without deep distress and great depression.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Let us therefore be determined to remember what we want today, that we may unify our thoughts and actions meaningfully, and achieve only what God would have us do this day.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"672#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, forgiveness is Your chosen means for our salvation.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Let us not forget today that we can have no will but Yours.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"672#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And thus our purpose must be Yours as well, if we would reach the peace You will for us.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"If I forget my goal I can be but confused, unsure of what I am, and thus conflicted in my actions. No one can serve contradicting goals and serve them well. Nor can he function without deep distress","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 257: Let me remember what my purpose is | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†257 ‚ÄúLet me remember what my purpo